{"tid":1268560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"促請警方報力清場","createTime":"2019-06-30T10:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T10:26:13.000Z","uid":207414,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1bbdaa6a4bded2799282e0edb1bd627fbfdf69a4","tid":1268560,"uid":207414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PYSX7TJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPYSX7TJ.png&h=1563a941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於本日於龍和道出現一群行為暴力的暴徒，本人黃心穎（已出軌）希望警方能夠使用最低限度的武力，以催淚彈、橡膠子彈、警棍甚至以實彈控制現場場面。<br />\n  若果警方不進行清場行動，會有包庇之嫌，本人不排除於明日7月1號，使用今天暴徒們採用同等的武力，對警方進行衝擊。若屆時警方使用過度武力鎮壓示威者，本人不排除會向外國勢力，對香港政府、對警方作出法律追究。<br />\n  最後本人想向香港特區政府、香港警察以及本日藍絲暴徒呼籲 我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雙重標準？"},{"pid":"a3d2bc34e46c8d200001949720fe241c9450411f","tid":1268560,"uid":207414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:22:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70406d42f91dd252db57333fc3c2b905df7d05fb","tid":1268560,"uid":207414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b469863450e508f070407f4978da5cb6b006821e","tid":1268560,"uid":207414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf3406441c968a92f007a8be9e9702dabf2ea3aa","tid":1268560,"uid":207414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:23:14.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暴力清場"},{"pid":"e9d81d0827706fbed7684035bc0a01ef78906dc0","tid":1268560,"uid":207414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:26:13.000Z","msg":"希望狗玩實彈<br />\n射撚死哂班垃圾藍絲狗"}]}